In MPEG2 umwandeln         : /etc/vdr/yacoto/yac.sh mpeg2
In XVid umwandeln          : /etc/vdr/yacoto/yac.sh xvid
In H264 umwandeln          : /etc/vdr/yacoto/yac.sh h264
In YouTube Format umwandeln: /etc/vdr/yacoto/yac.sh youtube
In MP3 umwandeln           : /etc/vdr/yacoto/yac.sh mp3
In OggVorbis umwandeln     : /etc/vdr/yacoto/yac.sh ogg
Status der Umwandlung      : /etc/vdr/yacoto/status.sh
Stream Information         : /etc/vdr/yacoto/setstream.sh mpeg2
  MP2 Spur1 waehlen        : /etc/vdr/yacoto/setstream.sh --mp=1
  MP2 Spur2 waehlen        : /etc/vdr/yacoto/setstream.sh --mp=2
  MP2 Spur3 waehlen        : /etc/vdr/yacoto/setstream.sh --mp=3
  DD Spur1 waehlen         : /etc/vdr/yacoto/setstream.sh --dd=1
  DD Spur2 waehlen         : /etc/vdr/yacoto/setstream.sh --dd=1
  Alle Tonspuren (crazy)   : /etc/vdr/yacoto/setstream.sh --all 
